-- Nokia Siemens wins $7 billion U.S. deal
-- 
-- Tue Jul 20, 2010 7:25am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/07/20/us-nokiasiemens-harbinger-idUSTRE66J1SP20100720

 

 HELSINKI  (Reuters) - Nokia Siemens Networks NSN.UL has won an eight-year deal worth more than $7 billion from Harbinger Capital's new LightSquared venture to build and operate a high-speed wireless network in the United States, LightSquared said on Tuesday. 

 (Reporting by  Tarmo Virki )